# @primo-brutality/ui

Neo-brutalist **React Native** component library (NativeWind v4). Read `AGENTS.md` and `llms.txt` for full context.

## Stack

- React Native primitives only (`View`, `Text`, `Pressable`) — never web elements
- Styling via NativeWind `className` and `brutal-*` design tokens
- Layout: prefer `YContainer`, `XContainer`, `Container`

## New components

Add `.tsx`, `.stories.tsx`, `.mdx`, and tests; export from `packages/ui/src/index.ts`; update `README.md` and `llms.txt`.

## Commands

`pnpm storybook` · `pnpm build` · `pnpm test`
